WEBVTT

01:39.440 --> 01:43.229
[Road to Success]

01:44.780 --> 01:47.940
[Episode 29]

02:07.870 --> 02:11.590
[Goodbye, my love]

02:27.740 --> 02:28.650
Professor Shu.

02:55.090 --> 03:01.400
[Goodbye, my love]

03:20.370 --> 03:26.650
[Goodbye, my love]

03:50.800 --> 03:52.400
How very careless of you.

03:53.079 --> 03:53.910
Many years have gone by,

03:53.910 --> 03:56.680
yet you've never noticed
the missing of a photo of yours.

03:56.680 --> 03:57.750
Xiang Zi,

03:58.800 --> 04:00.000
you have no shame at all.

04:00.000 --> 04:01.320
Is it really my fault?

04:01.350 --> 04:03.080
Lin Wanxing, why don't you
think about this—

04:03.080 --> 04:04.520
how did you get chosen

04:05.240 --> 04:06.630
from so many people?

04:06.650 --> 04:07.730
That's pure sophistry.

04:07.730 --> 04:09.350
Long before the candidate was decided,

04:09.350 --> 04:11.810
you had already
filmed that video in secret.

04:12.910 --> 04:14.590
Your words have actually reminded me.

04:14.590 --> 04:16.320
By disguising as you that time,

04:16.940 --> 04:19.680
I did discover many things.

04:32.810 --> 04:33.890
By the time

04:34.170 --> 04:35.200
I get hold of

04:35.240 --> 04:38.850
the surveillance video of a girl student's
rendezvous with a professor in a hotel,

04:38.850 --> 04:41.440
this will be a permanent stain
on your life.

04:42.400 --> 04:43.830
Lin Wanxing,

04:43.920 --> 04:46.540
I must destroy your reputation.

04:52.840 --> 04:55.230
Professor Shu, are you ready?

04:56.659 --> 04:58.280
Yes, I'm coming.

05:52.690 --> 05:54.030
[Intervention in quality inspection]

05:54.060 --> 05:55.350
[Measuring tool: multi-dimensional
evaluation framework]

06:00.650 --> 06:01.770
Unexpectedly,

06:02.110 --> 06:04.270
I found out Shu Yong's secret
on that occasion.

06:03.920 --> 06:08.060
[Sertraline Hydrochloride Tablets]

06:05.040 --> 06:06.080
See,

06:06.430 --> 06:08.190
even heaven is on my side.

06:10.720 --> 06:12.650
It turns out you are also a patient.

06:16.580 --> 06:17.870
Isn't it great?

06:18.390 --> 06:21.190
I really think all that has happened
is God's idea.

06:21.540 --> 06:22.770
Just by coincidence,

06:22.790 --> 06:24.600
I found out he had clinical depression.

06:24.600 --> 06:25.800
And so coincidentally,

06:25.800 --> 06:29.200
I was also the first one to discover
he had committed suicide.

06:31.180 --> 06:33.740
Shu Yong was really stupid.

06:34.390 --> 06:37.159
He'd rather take his life
than offer his spot to me.

06:37.159 --> 06:39.480
So, I decided to never let him
rest in peace.

06:39.480 --> 06:40.650
As for you...

06:41.159 --> 06:44.050
Everything started because of you.

06:44.159 --> 06:45.630
How could you
extricate yourself unscathed?

06:45.630 --> 06:46.480
How?

06:49.360 --> 06:51.360
Everyone likes you, Lin Wanxing,

06:51.450 --> 06:52.580
for being cheerful,

06:52.780 --> 06:54.020
youthful,

06:54.050 --> 06:54.930
and kind.

06:55.480 --> 06:56.950
So I decided to destroy you
with my own hands.

06:56.950 --> 06:58.070
I swore to push you into a mire

06:58.070 --> 07:00.400
and make sure
you could never get out of it.

07:05.480 --> 07:07.370
You can use your good looks

07:07.400 --> 07:08.990
to get whatever you want.

07:09.440 --> 07:10.910
I have my own ways too.

07:11.270 --> 07:12.310
I am not the one in the wrong.

07:12.310 --> 07:13.270
This whole world is wrong.

07:13.270 --> 07:14.680
Hypocrites like you are wrong.

07:14.680 --> 07:15.560
Xiang Zi!

07:17.720 --> 07:19.660
You've gone completely insane.

07:19.690 --> 07:21.150
So what?

07:22.190 --> 07:24.100
When this information is posted online

07:24.100 --> 07:25.660
and gaining traction...

07:25.720 --> 07:26.720
Gossip is a fearful thing.

07:26.720 --> 07:27.600
By then,

07:28.070 --> 07:29.950
your reputation will be ruined.

07:40.950 --> 07:42.870
So, is this a confession now?

07:42.980 --> 07:43.860
Yes.

07:44.450 --> 07:45.600
I admit

07:45.630 --> 07:47.070
that everything was my doing.

07:47.070 --> 07:48.270
I did all that.

07:48.830 --> 07:50.070
What can you do about it?

07:50.070 --> 07:51.800
What can you do about it?

07:55.950 --> 07:56.680
Are you okay?

08:13.960 --> 08:14.750
Wen Chengye!

08:17.830 --> 08:19.900
Did we not invite Ms. Lin over?

08:19.960 --> 08:20.890
No.

08:21.060 --> 08:23.040
So many things have happened lately.

08:23.040 --> 08:24.270
We've discussed and agreed

08:24.270 --> 08:26.270
that Ms. Lin should take a good rest.

08:28.510 --> 08:29.770
Let's start training.

08:39.080 --> 08:39.600
Look!

08:49.600 --> 08:50.330
How about...

08:50.750 --> 08:52.060
we go say hi?

08:53.600 --> 08:55.800
I don't think she wants to be disturbed.

08:59.390 --> 09:00.020
Coach.

09:00.040 --> 09:00.630
Coach!

09:00.630 --> 09:01.600
Hello, coach.

09:01.600 --> 09:02.790
Coach.

09:04.690 --> 09:06.200
Why is Ms. Lin

09:06.230 --> 09:08.230
running alone?

09:15.970 --> 09:16.860
Coach.

09:18.720 --> 09:20.650
Will we still have training today?

09:22.390 --> 09:24.050
You're all gathered here now.

09:24.320 --> 09:25.140
Start running then.

09:25.140 --> 09:26.690
Not until Ms. Lin finishes?

09:29.520 --> 09:30.310
Come on!

09:40.840 --> 09:42.600
Is a debauched woman like her truly

09:42.600 --> 09:43.870
worthy of all your efforts?

09:43.870 --> 09:45.240
Say it again, I dare you!

09:46.870 --> 09:49.480
Everything started because of you.

09:49.960 --> 09:51.480
How could you
extricate yourself unscathed?

09:51.480 --> 09:52.440
How?

09:54.240 --> 09:56.100
Everyone likes you, Lin Wanxing.

09:56.600 --> 09:58.200
So I decided to destroy you
with my own hands.

09:58.200 --> 09:59.320
I swore to push you into a mire

09:59.320 --> 10:01.650
and make sure
you could never get out of it.

10:01.870 --> 10:04.070
When this information is posted online

10:04.120 --> 10:05.000
and gaining traction...

10:05.000 --> 10:05.960
Gossip is a fearful thing.

10:05.960 --> 10:07.170
By then,

10:07.190 --> 10:08.990
your reputation will be ruined.

10:10.870 --> 10:11.910
He's just a dark and ugly rat

10:11.910 --> 10:13.670
hiding in a stinky gutter.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.240
Lin Wanxing,

10:15.600 --> 10:17.200
what is there to be afraid of?

10:24.790 --> 10:26.000
How interesting.

10:26.670 --> 10:29.330
The many difficulties
I used to deem as unsolvable

10:29.330 --> 10:30.600
now seem to be

10:30.720 --> 10:31.870
nothing at all.

10:34.270 --> 10:35.560
Wrong is wrong.

10:35.810 --> 10:38.010
No one should pay for others' mistakes.

11:10.830 --> 11:12.230
I'm going to sue Xiang Zi.

11:13.320 --> 11:14.790
I will have him pay the price

11:14.790 --> 11:15.920
for what he has done.

11:39.120 --> 11:40.000
Director Jia,

11:40.030 --> 11:42.630
we need a complete chain of evidence
for the lawsuit.

11:42.630 --> 11:44.200
Could you please try to recall

11:44.200 --> 11:46.390
how the situation escalated back then?

11:46.390 --> 11:47.850
We hope to find some clues.

11:49.120 --> 11:50.360
At that time,

11:50.630 --> 11:51.790
many people

11:51.960 --> 11:53.720
received an anonymous email.

11:54.750 --> 11:56.550
Then, overnight,

11:56.550 --> 11:58.150
things started to snowball.

11:58.840 --> 11:59.960
By the next day,

12:00.720 --> 12:02.650
the situation went out of control.

12:02.720 --> 12:03.750
Do you know

12:03.750 --> 12:05.260
who else received the email

12:05.260 --> 12:07.020
besides you?

12:07.080 --> 12:08.440
Many other people did,

12:09.320 --> 12:10.720
all of which were alumni.

12:10.860 --> 12:12.020
I guess...

12:12.720 --> 12:14.520
they amounted to over a hundred.

12:14.610 --> 12:16.570
Hello, I'd like to file a case.

12:16.740 --> 12:17.590
Okay.

12:17.620 --> 12:19.620
Please submit relevant materials.

12:21.490 --> 12:22.370
Okay.

12:24.960 --> 12:26.600
Thanks to Director Jia's help,

12:26.600 --> 12:28.360
we traced the source of the email.

12:28.360 --> 12:29.750
It's an abandoned account.

12:29.510 --> 12:31.600
[Lab Building, Yongchuan University]

12:30.510 --> 12:31.750
The IP address is located in...

12:31.750 --> 12:33.810
the lab building of your department.

12:33.930 --> 12:35.060
But we can't confirm

12:35.080 --> 12:36.610
Xiang Zi was the sender yet.

12:37.150 --> 12:39.870
More than one person
received that email, right?

12:39.870 --> 12:40.870
I'll go ask around on the forum

12:40.870 --> 12:43.530
to see if other receivers
have posted anything.

12:45.340 --> 12:46.940
[Shocking: A female top student came out
of a professor's room at midnight]

12:46.970 --> 12:48.810
[Check the video attached to the email]

12:48.900 --> 12:49.150
[Our professor always claims himself
to be a role model in the academic world]

12:49.180 --> 12:49.410
[But now there's a scandal about him]

12:49.430 --> 12:49.650
[This email has reached a wide audience]

12:49.670 --> 12:49.860
[It was even sent to
our department's group chat]

12:49.880 --> 12:50.250
[I got it too, such provocative content]

12:50.270 --> 12:50.460
[But there's no solid evidence]

12:50.720 --> 12:50.950
[This email has reached a wide audience]

12:50.970 --> 12:51.330
[It was even sent to
our department's group chat]

12:51.360 --> 12:51.540
[I didn't receive it, but my roommate did]

12:51.570 --> 12:51.750
[It looks like an insider wrote it]

12:53.790 --> 12:56.020
[I got the email, saying crap
like she knowingly became a mistress]

12:57.720 --> 13:02.960
[E Xiao Wu]

13:09.160 --> 13:10.460
I found a clue.

13:11.320 --> 13:13.080
Altogether,
over a hundred copies of this email

13:13.080 --> 13:14.120
were sent within three days

13:14.120 --> 13:15.480
from two IP addresses.

13:15.480 --> 13:17.360
One IP address is from the lab building
of Yongchuan University.

13:17.360 --> 13:19.000
But the other one can't be located yet.

13:19.000 --> 13:20.750
Yu Bo just told me that he found it.

13:20.750 --> 13:21.960
The other IP address traces back

13:21.960 --> 13:23.050
to Xiang Zi's home.

13:23.750 --> 13:24.840
The IP addresses are different,

13:24.840 --> 13:26.300
but the device is the same.

13:27.440 --> 13:28.770
Only Xiang Zi satisfies

13:29.240 --> 13:30.500
all these conditions.

13:31.840 --> 13:34.100
Please fill out this confirmation form.

13:38.980 --> 13:44.370
[The person to be served]
[Plaintiff's signature or stamp]

13:45.480 --> 13:46.320
Alright.

13:48.980 --> 13:53.050
[Notice of Acceptance
from the Hongjing City People's Court]

13:58.400 --> 14:00.000
The sea water feels so nice.

14:11.720 --> 14:13.240
Sometimes I felt like...

14:14.360 --> 14:16.230
I was a statue,

14:16.890 --> 14:18.640
being gazed at and judged

14:18.670 --> 14:19.760
by those people.

14:21.550 --> 14:23.610
I thought the more they slandered me,

14:24.360 --> 14:26.020
the straighter I had to stand.

14:27.370 --> 14:28.460
I must not lose.

14:30.750 --> 14:32.600
But now I've thought it through.

14:33.480 --> 14:36.100
I don't have to be so harsh on myself.

14:36.820 --> 14:38.260
Being alive itself

14:38.440 --> 14:40.060
is meaningful enough.

14:45.100 --> 14:47.630
There is no such thing as healing
in the world.

14:48.670 --> 14:51.360
Pain leaves scars in our hearts.

14:52.660 --> 14:55.320
So, amidst confusion and perplexity,
we need to

14:55.910 --> 14:57.710
hear the truest voice within us.

14:58.610 --> 15:01.020
It will help us overcome all difficulties

15:02.080 --> 15:04.010
and keep us company for a lifetime.

15:06.210 --> 15:08.410
This is what my therapist told me.

15:09.270 --> 15:10.730
Now, it's a gift to you too.

15:13.300 --> 15:14.060
Let's go!

15:15.120 --> 15:16.950
♪ Every night ♪

15:17.850 --> 15:19.820
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

15:20.740 --> 15:22.510
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

15:23.120 --> 15:25.330
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

15:26.500 --> 15:29.080
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

15:30.100 --> 15:31.860
♪ Because of your love ♪

15:32.790 --> 15:37.290
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

15:35.960 --> 15:37.720
Ivory,

15:37.720 --> 15:39.390
we are back.

15:42.960 --> 15:45.220
I'll go handle this in the kitchen first.

15:46.150 --> 15:48.240
Did you miss us?

15:48.240 --> 15:50.660
We'll take you to the beach
with us next time, alright?

15:50.660 --> 15:51.660
Good boy.

15:58.360 --> 15:58.840
Hello.

16:02.780 --> 16:03.840
Your dad's coming.

16:12.940 --> 16:13.750
Dad,

16:14.120 --> 16:15.320
what brings you here?

16:26.870 --> 16:27.910
Those are clothes.

16:27.910 --> 16:29.510
Clothes I bought for Ms. Lin.

16:30.730 --> 16:32.660
Why did you buy these many clothes?

16:32.750 --> 16:34.270
Ms. Lin is going to the battlefield soon.

16:34.270 --> 16:36.000
I'm here to deliver gear to her.

16:36.270 --> 16:38.120
She's going to court,

16:38.120 --> 16:39.280
not a fashion show.

16:39.390 --> 16:40.630
It's so typical of you,

16:40.630 --> 16:41.910
silly straight guy.

16:42.270 --> 16:44.000
Girls all like pretty clothes.

16:44.000 --> 16:45.120
Right, Ms. Lin?

16:46.480 --> 16:49.240
Anyway, I've brought the clothes here.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.240
Just accept them.

16:50.320 --> 16:54.050
Whether you'll wear them or not...
It's just a kind gesture from me.

16:54.200 --> 16:55.720
Thank you for such kindness, Uncle.

16:55.720 --> 16:57.790
Please don't go to any expense
on my account next time.

16:57.790 --> 16:59.080
You see, my tiny house

16:59.080 --> 17:00.740
can barely hold so many items.

17:01.270 --> 17:02.600
I can get you a new...

17:02.600 --> 17:05.880
Please don't buy me any houses,
either.

17:07.109 --> 17:08.240
Well, then, Ms. Lin,

17:08.240 --> 17:09.480
t-tell me what you like,

17:09.480 --> 17:10.740
and I'll buy it for you.

17:11.960 --> 17:13.160
Actually,

17:13.560 --> 17:14.550
I enjoy delicious food.

17:14.550 --> 17:15.160
How about this?

17:15.160 --> 17:16.750
I'll treat everyone to a meal next time.

17:16.750 --> 17:17.400
Sounds great.

17:17.400 --> 17:18.720
I'm a food enthusiast too.

17:18.720 --> 17:19.400
It's settled then.

17:19.400 --> 17:20.790
When you win this lawsuit,

17:20.790 --> 17:22.160
let's throw a victory party.

17:22.160 --> 17:24.400
We'll provide feasts
for three days and nights.

17:24.400 --> 17:26.440
-Thank you, Uncle.
-Cut that crap.

17:26.440 --> 17:29.270
Dad, aren't you going to
visit Yueyang Tower with Mom?

17:29.270 --> 17:31.440
Hurry up and memorize
the Record of Yueyang Tower.

17:31.440 --> 17:32.550
I did forget about it.

17:32.550 --> 17:33.280
You did, huh?

17:33.590 --> 17:34.920
Had better get a move on.

17:35.270 --> 17:36.350
Bye bye then!

17:37.680 --> 17:39.270
Don't buy clothes for her
with your taste again.

17:39.270 --> 17:40.000
Got it.

17:44.640 --> 17:47.160
Your dad has a more lovely personality
than you.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.350
It's rare to see a wealthy

17:48.350 --> 17:50.030
young man's father this amiable.

17:50.030 --> 17:50.680
How do you know

17:50.680 --> 17:52.920
I won't be more lovable than him
when I get older?

17:52.920 --> 17:53.790
Ms. Lin,

17:53.790 --> 17:54.990
you just wait and see.

17:55.720 --> 17:56.350
Okay.

17:57.590 --> 17:59.160
By the way, how's your preparation
of materials?

17:59.160 --> 18:00.030
Almost done.

18:00.030 --> 18:01.680
This time, I'll make sure

18:01.680 --> 18:03.210
that scumbag is convicted.

18:03.830 --> 18:05.240
I'm more concerned about your side.

18:05.240 --> 18:06.160
Xiangzhen Lingshi

18:06.160 --> 18:08.270
advanced as the top of Group D.

18:08.270 --> 18:09.850
They are not to be underestimated.

18:09.850 --> 18:11.080
Don't worry.

18:11.110 --> 18:12.310
I'm not afraid at all.

18:12.790 --> 18:13.640
Let's cook!

18:15.750 --> 18:17.350
Time to do some cooking.

18:48.720 --> 18:50.720
This is an announcement of court rules.

18:49.030 --> 18:55.750
[Courtroom No. 6 for Cross-regional Cases]

18:50.920 --> 18:53.550
First, all personnel
present at the court session

18:53.550 --> 18:55.070
shall obey the directions

18:55.070 --> 18:56.920
of the presiding judge or the sole judge,

18:56.920 --> 18:58.440
and observe judicial etiquette.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.770
Court is now in session!

19:01.510 --> 19:02.550
Mr. Presiding Judge,

19:02.550 --> 19:05.380
the plaintiff now presents
the first set of evidence.

19:05.380 --> 19:06.310
This set of evidence

19:06.310 --> 19:08.720
consists of the notarized preservation
of electronic evidence

19:08.620 --> 19:10.640
[Notarial Certificate]

19:08.720 --> 19:11.070
from the plaintiff's
extinguished alumnus's email accounts,

19:11.070 --> 19:13.070
as well as other supporting materials.

19:13.070 --> 19:14.310
There are 135 emails

19:14.330 --> 19:16.180
in total.

19:15.970 --> 19:18.620
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Plaintiff]

19:16.310 --> 19:18.200
The purpose of exhibiting such evidence

19:18.200 --> 19:20.000
is to prove that the defendant committed

19:20.000 --> 19:22.500
an infringement and caused damages
to the plaintiff.

19:22.340 --> 19:26.430
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Plaintiff]

19:22.550 --> 19:23.550
We can see here

19:23.550 --> 19:25.030
that the emails are filled

19:25.030 --> 19:27.640
with insulting remarks
and defamatory information

19:27.640 --> 19:28.640
directed at

19:28.640 --> 19:30.160
the plaintiff, Ms. Lin Wanxing.

19:30.160 --> 19:30.790
For example,

19:30.790 --> 19:34.070
the fabricated claim
of an improper relationship

19:34.070 --> 19:36.400
between the plaintiff and her supervisor,
with highly insulting remarks

19:36.400 --> 19:39.550
to gravely damage
the plaintiff's right to reputation.

19:39.550 --> 19:40.160
Moreover,

19:39.630 --> 19:43.630
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Plaintiff]

19:40.160 --> 19:41.440
the IP addresses from which

19:41.440 --> 19:44.400
the emails were sent both
trace back to the defendant's computer.

19:44.400 --> 19:47.160
In addition, the sender's email account

19:47.160 --> 19:50.270
is both registered to and used
by the defendant.

19:50.270 --> 19:53.030
Besides, the alumni
who received these emails

19:53.030 --> 19:54.640
come from all walks of life.

19:54.640 --> 19:56.270
They have extensive social connections,

19:56.270 --> 19:57.790
and each of them is a renowned figure

19:57.790 --> 19:59.390
in their respective fields.

19:59.550 --> 20:00.400
These emails

20:00.400 --> 20:03.640
not only damaged
Ms. Lin Wanxing's personal reputation,

20:03.640 --> 20:05.550
but also caused adverse effects

20:05.550 --> 20:07.310
in the field of her profession,

20:07.310 --> 20:10.920
leading to a significant drop
in the plaintiff's social evaluation,

20:07.390 --> 20:13.670
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Plaintiff]

20:10.920 --> 20:14.030
and causing tremendous mental distress.

20:14.030 --> 20:16.230
The emails also brought
substantial negative impacts

20:16.230 --> 20:19.090
on the plaintiff's
academic studies and research.

20:20.640 --> 20:21.920
The defendant may

20:21.920 --> 20:24.790
cross-examine
the first set of evidence now.

20:25.300 --> 20:32.750
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Defendant]

20:25.400 --> 20:29.310
Mr. Presiding Judge, we have no objection
to the authenticity of the evidence

20:29.310 --> 20:30.920
submitted by the plaintiff,

20:30.920 --> 20:33.270
but we have doubts about its relevance.

20:32.830 --> 20:35.880
[Authorized Representative
for Oral Argument] [Plaintiff]

20:33.270 --> 20:34.270
It is our belief

20:34.270 --> 20:36.000
that the IP addresses
from which the emails were sent

20:36.000 --> 20:37.920
being traceable to my client's computer

20:37.920 --> 20:39.270
cannot directly prove

20:39.270 --> 20:42.200
that the emails were sent
by Mr. Xiang Zi himself.

20:42.200 --> 20:43.640
Yongchuan University's
Information Service Center

20:43.640 --> 20:46.790
provides email services
for all teachers and students.

20:46.790 --> 20:49.310
Mr. Xiang Zi is the registered owner
of the sender's email account,

20:49.310 --> 20:52.640
but there is a possibility
that the account was hacked.

20:52.640 --> 20:55.270
Therefore, the plaintiff's conclusion

20:55.270 --> 20:57.640
of my client being the anonymous sender
of the emails

20:57.640 --> 20:59.160
is not objective.

20:59.160 --> 21:03.000
The defendant suggests the possibility
of the account being hacked,

21:03.000 --> 21:05.550
but provides no evidence or materials

21:05.550 --> 21:07.720
to support this claim.

21:07.720 --> 21:10.830
Mr. Presiding Judge, the defendant
would like to state the facts again.

21:10.830 --> 21:13.350
The defendant did not insult or defame
the plaintiff.

21:13.350 --> 21:15.160
The fact that Ms. Lin Wanxing,

21:15.160 --> 21:18.240
as a woman of attractive appearance,

21:18.240 --> 21:19.830
used her good looks

21:19.830 --> 21:21.550
to seduce an academic authority

21:21.550 --> 21:24.540
for improper academic benefits
is not to be ignored.

21:24.570 --> 21:27.480
My client did not fabricate this claim,

21:27.480 --> 21:30.390
but revealed it as a fact
based on the truth.

21:30.410 --> 21:31.610
The defendant rests.

21:32.070 --> 21:34.960
The plaintiff may continue
to present evidence now.

21:34.960 --> 21:37.200
Mr. Presiding Judge,
please have the court noted

21:37.200 --> 21:40.380
the statement just made
by the defendant's representative.

21:40.380 --> 21:41.480
To a certain extent,

21:41.480 --> 21:43.120
that statement
made by the defendant's counsel

21:43.120 --> 21:44.440
already constitutes

21:44.440 --> 21:47.960
an admission of the defendant being
the sender of the emails in question.

21:47.960 --> 21:48.590
Moreover,

21:48.590 --> 21:52.260
by doing so, the defendant once again
threw insulting and defamatory remarks

21:52.260 --> 21:53.720
at the plaintiff in court.

21:54.550 --> 21:55.310
Now,

21:55.310 --> 21:58.440
the plaintiff shall present
the second set of evidence.

21:58.550 --> 22:00.720
This set of evidence includes

22:00.720 --> 22:01.590
clothes and a wig.

22:01.590 --> 22:02.440
All of these

22:02.440 --> 22:05.750
are exactly belongings
of the defendant, Mr. Xiang Zi.

22:08.830 --> 22:10.720
What is shown on the screen now

22:10.720 --> 22:11.640
is a photo of my client's

22:11.640 --> 22:14.070
from when she was in university.

22:14.070 --> 22:16.230
A careful comparison can easily reveal

22:16.230 --> 22:17.880
that these clothes owned by the defendant,

22:17.880 --> 22:19.310
Mr. Xiang Zi, and the style of his wig

22:19.310 --> 22:20.830
exactly match my client's

22:20.830 --> 22:22.750
outfits and hairstyle

22:22.750 --> 22:24.640
during her university years.

22:24.640 --> 22:25.680
Mr. Presiding Judge,

22:25.680 --> 22:27.310
it is my opinion that the opposing counsel

22:27.310 --> 22:29.350
is creating confusion with coincidences.

22:29.350 --> 22:31.750
Indeed, these clothes belong to my client.

22:31.760 --> 22:34.550
But this can only prove
that he has some special hobbies.

22:34.550 --> 22:37.410
It has no direct relevance
to this case whatsoever.

22:37.440 --> 22:38.200
Mr. Presiding Judge,

22:38.200 --> 22:41.330
please allow me
to present the third set of evidence now.

22:42.820 --> 22:44.160
This set of evidence

22:43.430 --> 22:46.120
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

22:44.160 --> 22:45.480
consists of two videos.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.510
One

22:46.140 --> 22:49.300
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

22:46.510 --> 22:49.270
is about an academic exchange meeting.

22:49.270 --> 22:51.240
We can see from it that the defendant

22:51.240 --> 22:52.030
displays

22:52.030 --> 22:55.350
several habitual movements
with personal characteristics.

22:52.110 --> 22:53.410
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

22:53.430 --> 22:55.000
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

22:55.350 --> 22:56.640
However, my client does not have

22:56.640 --> 22:58.970
such characteristic habits of movement.

22:59.350 --> 23:00.790
Now, let's review the second video,

23:00.790 --> 23:02.940
namely the one involved with this case.

23:02.940 --> 23:04.070
It can be clearly seen

23:04.070 --> 23:05.550
that those habitual movements

23:05.550 --> 23:06.900
exclusive to the defendant

23:06.900 --> 23:08.960
are actually made by the person
in this video,

23:08.960 --> 23:10.540
who is alleged to be my client.

23:10.540 --> 23:11.630
It thus shows

23:11.680 --> 23:13.390
the person in this video

23:13.420 --> 23:15.000
is not my client,

23:15.000 --> 23:16.800
but the defendant, Mr. Xiang Zi.

23:32.930 --> 23:37.040
[Serve the people
through impartial justice]

23:40.070 --> 23:40.960
Hey.

23:40.960 --> 23:41.640
It's been so long.

23:41.640 --> 23:43.200
How come the trial isn't over yet?

23:43.200 --> 23:44.390
Let's wait a bit longer.

23:44.390 --> 23:45.650
It should be over soon.

23:47.970 --> 23:48.790
Don't worry.

23:50.070 --> 23:51.440
Ms. Lin

23:52.160 --> 23:53.360
will definitely win.

23:57.240 --> 24:01.060
[Serve the people
through impartial justice]

24:01.270 --> 24:03.200
This concludes the oral argument.

24:03.240 --> 24:05.270
According to the Civil Procedure Law

24:05.270 --> 24:07.200
of the People's Republic of China,

24:07.270 --> 24:10.510
both parties involved have the right
to make final statements.

24:10.510 --> 24:13.110
The plaintiff
shall address the court first.

24:19.790 --> 24:21.480
Honorable Mr. Presiding Judge,

24:21.480 --> 24:23.010
everyone present in court,

24:23.720 --> 24:24.780
frankly speaking,

24:25.070 --> 24:26.590
suing Xiang Zi

24:26.590 --> 24:28.240
is no easy task for me,

24:29.190 --> 24:30.720
because whenever I see him,

24:31.270 --> 24:32.590
I am reminded of all the malice

24:32.590 --> 24:34.310
aimed at me over these years.

24:37.180 --> 24:38.770
I was once rather pertubed.

24:39.440 --> 24:41.000
I wondered what would happen to me

24:41.000 --> 24:42.330
if I lost today's trial.

24:43.250 --> 24:45.050
Will what happened two years ago

24:45.110 --> 24:46.380
repeat itself?

24:51.940 --> 24:54.140
It took me altogether 19 years
to walk the path

24:54.140 --> 24:56.920
from elementary school
to obtaining my master's degree.

24:56.920 --> 24:58.780
But all my effort in those 19 years

24:59.080 --> 25:00.580
and everything else I had

25:00.790 --> 25:02.090
was easily ruined

25:02.240 --> 25:03.920
by a single sex rumor

25:04.040 --> 25:06.770
and some so-called evidence
riddled with flaws.

25:08.900 --> 25:10.380
People like Xiang Zi

25:10.400 --> 25:12.400
know too well how to destroy a woman.

25:12.720 --> 25:15.720
Dyeing the hair pink
is equal to improper conduct.

25:15.740 --> 25:18.490
Wearing a short skirt
is equal to an attempt at seduction.

25:18.490 --> 25:20.530
Pretty women are considered temptresses.

25:20.530 --> 25:22.690
Dressing plainly means
this woman is just wild on the inside.

25:22.690 --> 25:24.820
Everyone loves reading gossip.

25:24.850 --> 25:26.930
As long as a woman is once rumored
to be a slut,

25:26.930 --> 25:28.250
she always will be one.

25:31.140 --> 25:32.740
I do not deem myself fragile.

25:32.910 --> 25:33.880
Two years ago,

25:34.830 --> 25:36.200
I stood at a rooftop.

25:36.370 --> 25:37.700
But I didn't jump off it,

25:38.830 --> 25:40.800
because I thought of my family and friends

25:40.800 --> 25:41.860
who love me dearly.

25:43.880 --> 25:46.140
I spent two years getting back on my feet.

25:48.080 --> 25:50.210
I gathered all the necessary evidence

25:50.660 --> 25:53.120
and proved Xiang Zi fabricated everything.

25:53.950 --> 25:55.340
But what's the point?

25:56.790 --> 25:58.390
When I was back to the office,

25:58.710 --> 26:01.310
all my colleagues
were still talking about me,

26:01.430 --> 26:03.760
Lin Wanxing, of being a promiscuous woman

26:03.820 --> 26:05.490
who seduced her supervisor.

26:16.400 --> 26:18.330
The defendant once said this to me:

26:18.820 --> 26:20.490
A broken butterfly

26:21.830 --> 26:23.400
can never fly again.

26:27.260 --> 26:28.430
However, today,

26:28.610 --> 26:30.810
I'm standing here for one exact reason:

26:31.170 --> 26:32.970
I must announce to you, Xiang Zi,

26:33.430 --> 26:34.630
that I do not fear you.

26:34.960 --> 26:37.770
On behalf of every woman
being victimized by sexual rumors,

26:37.770 --> 26:39.630
I am here to tell you loud and clear

26:40.340 --> 26:42.340
that we do not fear you and your kind.

26:46.840 --> 26:47.880
Your failure

26:48.600 --> 26:50.730
resulted from your own incompetence.

26:50.750 --> 26:52.950
You crushed the woman you couldn't get.

26:53.160 --> 26:54.920
You destroyed the competitor
you couldn't beat.

26:54.920 --> 26:56.370
Each and every thing you did

26:56.370 --> 26:58.900
was only to conceal
your inadequacy and jealousy.

26:58.900 --> 26:59.730
And I...

27:00.720 --> 27:03.780
Why should I ever fear someone
so incompetent like you?

27:06.790 --> 27:09.040
The fact that I'm standing here today

27:09.210 --> 27:10.740
means you've already lost.

27:11.590 --> 27:14.300
Lin Wanxing,
you're slandering my character!

27:14.830 --> 27:16.770
Defendant, control your emotions.

27:16.770 --> 27:18.510
Do people like you
who get by on your looks

27:18.510 --> 27:19.820
even know anything about academics?

27:19.820 --> 27:22.290
Defendant, please watch your language.

27:22.320 --> 27:23.570
Insults and abusive language
are not allowed.

27:23.570 --> 27:25.160
You are hereby reprimanded by this court.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.480
She slandered me!

27:26.480 --> 27:27.440
Why do you only hush me,

27:27.440 --> 27:28.400
but not her?

27:28.400 --> 27:30.790
This woman climbed her way up
by seducing professors.

27:30.790 --> 27:32.650
Who is she to call me incompetent?

27:32.750 --> 27:35.440
The malice some people in this society
have towards women

27:35.440 --> 27:37.640
once made me lose the courage to live.

27:38.120 --> 27:39.520
But now I have realized.

27:39.880 --> 27:41.110
People like Xiang Zi

27:41.480 --> 27:43.650
are living in the sewer like rats.

27:43.830 --> 27:45.550
They're trying to drag us down

27:45.570 --> 27:46.920
and splash mud all over us.

27:46.920 --> 27:49.450
But they are the ones
who will always be dirty.

27:49.480 --> 27:51.480
We should never punish ourselves.

27:51.960 --> 27:53.110
Plaintiff,

27:53.110 --> 27:55.720
please restrict your statement
to the case.

27:55.720 --> 27:57.850
Refrain from inappropriate wording.

27:59.350 --> 28:01.150
Honorable Mr. Presiding Judge,

28:01.640 --> 28:03.220
this concludes my statement.

28:03.220 --> 28:05.220
Lin Wanxing, who did you call a rat?

28:05.270 --> 28:06.720
Who did you call a rat?

28:06.720 --> 28:08.160
Lin Wanxing, I'm telling you,

28:08.160 --> 28:09.000
if I say you're a slut,

28:09.000 --> 28:11.550
-you'll always be a slut!
-For violating courtroom discipline,

28:11.550 --> 28:12.960
the defendant is ordered to leave.

28:12.960 --> 28:13.750
Believe it or not,

28:13.750 --> 28:14.510
I can ruin you a million times

28:14.510 --> 28:15.740
now that I've done it once already!

28:15.740 --> 28:16.670
Just you wait.

28:16.720 --> 28:18.250
Lin Wanxing, just you wait!

28:18.830 --> 28:19.960
Just you wait!

28:23.400 --> 28:24.680
Court is adjourned.

28:24.960 --> 28:26.510
The verdict will be pronounced

28:26.510 --> 28:27.970
after the panel's review.

28:33.810 --> 28:36.880
[Strive to ensure the people]

28:36.900 --> 28:39.910
[Feel justice and fairness
in every judicial case]

28:44.550 --> 28:45.220
How did it go?

28:45.220 --> 28:45.890
-What's the verdict?
-How did it go?

28:45.890 --> 28:47.690
-How was it?
-What's the ruling?

28:57.480 --> 29:00.400
According to the Civil Code
of the People's Republic of China,

29:00.400 --> 29:02.520
and relevant laws and regulations,

29:03.000 --> 29:05.070
this court finds that Xiang Zi's actions

29:05.070 --> 29:07.400
infringed upon
Lin Wanxing's right to reputation.

29:07.400 --> 29:09.830
Xiang Zi shall assume liability
for such infringement

29:09.830 --> 29:11.830
and eliminate the adverse effects.

29:13.680 --> 29:15.240
The judgment is as follows.

29:15.240 --> 29:18.730
One, Xiang Zi shall immediately
cease the infringement,

29:18.760 --> 29:21.210
and apologize to Lin Wanxing in writing

29:21.240 --> 29:22.480
on the notice board

29:22.480 --> 29:24.830
of Yongchuan University's
official website,

29:22.960 --> 29:28.640
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

29:25.110 --> 29:27.710
the defendant's verified Weibo account,

29:27.920 --> 29:29.510
and the People's Court Daily

29:29.230 --> 29:33.690
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

29:29.510 --> 29:33.770
for five consecutive days, starting
from the effective date of this ruling.

29:35.840 --> 29:40.790
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

29:36.350 --> 29:38.610
The content shall be approved
by this court before release.

29:38.610 --> 29:40.790
If Xiang Zi refuses
to comply with the judgement,

29:40.790 --> 29:42.750
this court will publish

29:41.770 --> 29:47.200
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

29:42.750 --> 29:45.070
the main content of this judgment online.

29:45.070 --> 29:47.400
-The expenses will be paid by Xiang Zi.
-To Ms. Lin Wanxing,

29:47.400 --> 29:49.480
I deeply regret my ignorance
and foolishness.

29:48.780 --> 29:54.490
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

29:49.480 --> 29:52.110
-Second, this court hopes
-I also sincerely apologize for causing

29:52.110 --> 29:54.830
-this trial and judgement can serve
-mental distress and reputational damage

29:54.830 --> 29:56.960
-as a warning to the public
-to Ms. Lin Wanxing. I cordially hope to

29:54.880 --> 29:57.870
[Apology]

29:55.220 --> 30:00.020
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

29:56.990 --> 29:59.240
-to respect others' right to reputation,
-to be forgiven by her. Out of prejudice

29:59.240 --> 30:03.000
-to never make or spread false claims,
-and impulse, I not only hurt her dignity,

30:01.690 --> 30:06.840
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

30:03.000 --> 30:06.000
-and to uphold a good social order
-but also fueled the cyberbullying

30:06.000 --> 30:07.160
-and a sound online environment together.
-against her.

30:07.160 --> 30:08.240
Ms. Lin Wanxing was therefore

30:07.820 --> 30:12.950
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

30:08.240 --> 30:09.370
subjected to public pressure

30:09.370 --> 30:11.790
far beyond
what an ordinary person could bear,

30:11.790 --> 30:14.000
even to the extent
of affecting her studies and life.

30:13.840 --> 30:19.730
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

30:15.070 --> 30:17.130
I am to blame for these consequences.

30:17.440 --> 30:19.640
Thinking back about what I said and did,

30:19.750 --> 30:21.510
I feel deeply ashamed and remorseful.

30:20.450 --> 30:26.220
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

30:22.400 --> 30:25.160
I am willing to bear
all due responsibilities for the incident,

30:25.160 --> 30:26.510
and publicly promise

30:26.510 --> 30:29.010
to reflect on and amend for my wrongdoing
with actual actions,

30:26.900 --> 30:32.510
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

30:29.550 --> 30:31.960
so as not to make the same mistake.

30:33.350 --> 30:35.070
Apologies given by Xiang Zi,

30:33.370 --> 30:38.610
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

30:35.830 --> 30:39.510
on March 30, 2026.

30:39.510 --> 30:40.960
Meanwhile, according to the police,

30:39.590 --> 30:43.350
[Hongjing News]

30:39.660 --> 30:45.240
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

30:40.960 --> 30:43.550
Xiang Zi is suspected of inciting a minor
to commit suicide overseas.

30:43.550 --> 30:44.510
The case has now come to light.

30:44.510 --> 30:47.000
Local police have started conducting
an investigation.

30:45.980 --> 30:51.720
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

30:47.000 --> 30:48.400
If judicial authorities determine

30:48.400 --> 30:51.030
that the evidence is sufficient
to prove him guilty,

30:51.030 --> 30:53.200
Xiang Zi will possibly
face legal punishment.

30:52.500 --> 30:58.560
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

30:53.200 --> 30:54.400
Just as I pointed out before,

30:54.400 --> 30:55.830
in this case,

30:55.830 --> 30:57.200
why was my client tagged

30:57.200 --> 30:59.070
with those unfounded labels?

30:59.070 --> 31:00.400
Here's the reason.

30:59.160 --> 31:04.860
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

30:59.440 --> 31:02.400
[A lesson on law by Mr. Lyu]

31:00.400 --> 31:01.830
The society is constraining women

31:01.830 --> 31:04.510
with stereotypical frameworks.

31:04.510 --> 31:05.270
Beauty

31:05.270 --> 31:06.400
has become a sin.

31:06.320 --> 31:10.740
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

31:06.400 --> 31:08.510
Being talented is misinterpreted
as being manipulative.

31:06.750 --> 31:10.620
[A lesson on law by Mr. Lyu]

31:08.510 --> 31:10.750
It is precisely these social prejudices

31:10.750 --> 31:12.720
that restrict women's

31:12.720 --> 31:14.650
healthy development in this society

31:14.650 --> 31:16.960
and deprive women of the dignity

31:16.980 --> 31:18.370
they deserve.

31:22.790 --> 31:24.320
It's nice to live in a villa.

31:24.750 --> 31:26.760
But one has to climb stairs.

31:27.110 --> 31:29.110
Why don't you spend some money
renovating the place,

31:29.110 --> 31:30.710
like installing an elevator?

31:30.710 --> 31:32.840
You really need some cardio exercise.

31:32.960 --> 31:34.720
I knew you would say that.

31:34.720 --> 31:36.070
No matter

31:36.070 --> 31:37.720
what kind of adversity you are in,

31:37.720 --> 31:39.440
you are not fighting alone.

31:39.440 --> 31:40.270
You need to learn to

31:40.270 --> 31:42.150
-seek help from others.
-Mr. Lyu's words are very powerful.

31:42.150 --> 31:44.200
-Oh, right.
-Only by countering the attacks head-on...

31:44.200 --> 31:47.110
I've finished the preliminary process
for the establishment

31:47.110 --> 31:49.790
of the legal aid fund for women
that you're trying to set up.

31:49.790 --> 31:51.650
The expense was too high, though.

31:52.550 --> 31:54.200
Money should go to where it's needed most.

31:54.200 --> 31:54.960
I believe Mr. Lyu's words

31:54.960 --> 31:55.830
Before the completion...

31:55.830 --> 31:58.070
have made a very positive impression
on the audience.

31:58.070 --> 31:59.000
Thank you so much.

31:59.000 --> 31:59.790
Come on.

32:04.350 --> 32:06.150
Rare for you to open a beer for me.

32:07.720 --> 32:10.650
Have you switched careers
and become a drunkard now?

32:10.750 --> 32:11.790
Cheers!

32:11.790 --> 32:12.850
Don't drink alone.

32:42.720 --> 32:43.510
Dad,

32:44.510 --> 32:46.510
the boys you always talked about

32:47.200 --> 32:48.350
are here to visit you now.

32:48.080 --> 32:54.090
[Tomb of Jiangjun, A Loving Father]

32:58.070 --> 32:58.880
Coach,

32:59.830 --> 33:01.200
we made it to the finals.

33:02.360 --> 33:03.450
You said

33:03.670 --> 33:06.590
we must treat you to hot pot
when we won the tournament.

33:06.590 --> 33:08.790
We've saved a place for you on the table.

33:09.750 --> 33:12.010
Hope you wouldn't resent the spicy food.

33:12.890 --> 33:13.680
Jiang,

33:14.110 --> 33:15.110
I wish you could

33:15.880 --> 33:17.960
come watch us play again.

33:18.640 --> 33:19.510
Coach Jiang,

33:21.480 --> 33:24.000
I can curve the ball really well now.

33:26.200 --> 33:28.000
It's a shame you can't see it now.

33:28.590 --> 33:30.320
With or without your presence,

33:31.270 --> 33:33.730
we'll do our best in every game
in the future.

33:35.340 --> 33:36.140
Coach...

33:38.200 --> 33:39.550
We're still together.

33:41.180 --> 33:43.090
May you rest in peace in heaven.

33:42.930 --> 33:48.790
[Tomb of Jiangjun, A Loving Father]

33:45.210 --> 33:46.550
Spend more time
with Mr. Lin and Mrs. Lin

33:46.550 --> 33:48.210
playing chess or stuff there.

33:49.790 --> 33:50.590
Jiang,

33:51.110 --> 33:53.240
we're all great football players now.

33:53.730 --> 33:55.790
You could boast about us everywhere.

33:58.160 --> 33:58.960
Jiang,

34:00.510 --> 34:02.420
please don't take the nonsense

34:02.690 --> 34:04.360
I said before to heart.

34:05.750 --> 34:06.590
I was wrong.

34:07.480 --> 34:08.230
Jiang,

34:10.080 --> 34:12.409
I've grown five more centimeters taller.

34:13.590 --> 34:16.989
My vertical jump is three centimeters
over the standard now.

34:19.020 --> 34:20.270
In the past,

34:20.800 --> 34:22.110
we were silly

34:22.110 --> 34:23.440
and ignorant.

34:24.840 --> 34:27.040
We even hated you for leaving us behind.

34:28.880 --> 34:29.710
Coach,

34:30.190 --> 34:31.000
sorry.

34:32.590 --> 34:34.070
Please don't be mad at us.

34:39.510 --> 34:40.320
Alright.

34:41.630 --> 34:43.429
He would never be mad at you guys.

34:46.800 --> 34:49.000
Instead, he would be proud of all of you.

34:50.880 --> 34:51.710
Coach Jiang,

34:52.280 --> 34:53.800
we really miss you a lot.

35:15.740 --> 35:21.160
[Tomb of Jiangjun, A Loving Father]

36:08.710 --> 36:10.230
When did you come out here?

36:10.230 --> 36:11.760
There wasn't a sound at all.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.840
What wishes did you make?

36:17.440 --> 36:19.700
Do you see the brightest star over there?

36:21.590 --> 36:22.800
It's called Alioth.

36:23.550 --> 36:26.110
In childhood, my grandpa told me

36:26.360 --> 36:27.800
that when I grew up,

36:28.360 --> 36:29.360
he and grandma

36:29.360 --> 36:31.030
would move to that planet

36:31.030 --> 36:32.290
as my guardian angels.

36:34.320 --> 36:35.480
Well...

36:36.030 --> 36:37.760
What did you say to them?

36:39.230 --> 36:42.030
I told them that I won the case,

36:42.030 --> 36:44.190
and that they shouldn't worry anymore.

36:44.190 --> 36:45.360
From now on,

36:45.880 --> 36:48.080
my life will only get better and better.

36:50.030 --> 36:50.880
What else?

36:55.510 --> 36:56.880
I also said...

37:04.230 --> 37:05.560
I'd rather not tell you.

37:07.030 --> 37:09.090
Never mind if you don't want to say it.

37:09.710 --> 37:11.970
Let's eat at my parents' place tomorrow.

38:00.670 --> 38:02.840
Seriously, don't you think
you two are dressed

38:02.840 --> 38:05.070
too casually for such a formal occasion?

38:05.070 --> 38:05.730
Look at you.

38:06.960 --> 38:07.840
Really?

38:09.480 --> 38:12.130
But you are dressed quite formally.

38:12.590 --> 38:15.480
Are you going to propose marriage
at my home, dressed like this?

38:15.480 --> 38:17.540
Has Wang Tian agreed to marry you yet?

38:18.030 --> 38:20.000
She will say yes sooner or later.

38:23.670 --> 38:24.360
Come on.

38:24.360 --> 38:25.160
Let's go home.

38:37.320 --> 38:38.480
You're back, Fa.

38:38.480 --> 38:39.320
Auntie Rong.

38:40.030 --> 38:41.440
-This must be Wanxing, right?
-Auntie Rong.

38:41.440 --> 38:42.920
Change into the slippers over there.

38:42.920 --> 38:43.710
Thanks.

38:44.760 --> 38:45.220
Come on.

38:49.920 --> 38:50.670
Dad!

38:53.710 --> 38:55.070
Welcome.

38:55.070 --> 38:55.630
Hello, Uncle.

38:55.630 --> 38:57.590
Ms. Lin, I was looking forward
to your arrival.

38:57.590 --> 38:58.920
Now, you're finally here.

38:58.920 --> 39:01.540
Uncle, just call me Wanxing.

39:01.670 --> 39:03.030
Sure, Wanxing.

39:03.030 --> 39:05.550
Uncle, call me Bo if you like.

39:06.190 --> 39:07.360
Why did you come here too?

39:07.360 --> 39:09.190
Here you are,
just a small gesture from me.

39:09.190 --> 39:11.190
No, no. I don't eat junk like that.

39:11.190 --> 39:13.150
No, these are the latest products.

39:13.150 --> 39:14.840
They bring great benefits to the elderly.

39:14.840 --> 39:15.710
What do you mean?

39:15.710 --> 39:17.870
Are you saying I'm very old now?

39:17.890 --> 39:20.440
No, I'm not. See, you're middle-aged
and getting old.

39:20.440 --> 39:21.150
It's time you...

39:21.150 --> 39:22.550
-It's time for what?
-For t-taking care

39:22.550 --> 39:23.840
o-of your health.

39:24.280 --> 39:24.630
Dad.

39:24.830 --> 39:27.960
[Spicy wheat gluten strips]

39:25.400 --> 39:28.330
Wanxing bought these spicy strips
for you in secret.

39:28.330 --> 39:29.210
Really?

39:32.320 --> 39:33.940
Listen, Uncle.

39:34.150 --> 39:36.110
Spicy strips provides zero nutrition.

39:36.110 --> 39:37.110
Look at this,

39:37.440 --> 39:39.850
Reishi mushroom, the finest of its kind.

39:40.070 --> 39:40.590
Forget about it.

39:40.590 --> 39:41.670
My nose bled after eating

39:41.670 --> 39:42.800
the stuff you gave me last time.

39:42.800 --> 39:45.030
Are you trying to get me hospitalized
this time?

39:45.030 --> 39:46.030
-Last time...
-What about it?

39:46.030 --> 39:46.550
What about it, huh?

39:46.550 --> 39:47.960
You just ate too much last time.

39:47.960 --> 39:49.220
That was not really...

39:49.320 --> 39:51.320
How did you know I like spicy strips?

39:51.550 --> 39:52.590
Wang Fa told me that.

39:52.590 --> 39:53.030
See?

39:53.030 --> 39:54.920
Wanxing knows me so well.

39:55.480 --> 39:56.440
Stash them for me.

39:56.440 --> 39:57.840
Don't let your mother find them.

39:57.840 --> 39:58.720
Rest assured.

39:59.840 --> 40:01.900
Uncle, these flowers are for you too.

40:02.360 --> 40:04.400
Flowers too? How thoughtful of you.

40:04.400 --> 40:06.030
I brought flowers as well.

40:06.440 --> 40:07.190
Look.

40:12.710 --> 40:14.170
Still, lilies are better.

40:14.550 --> 40:15.940
Elegant and tasteful.

40:15.970 --> 40:17.840
Roses are just too tacky.

40:20.840 --> 40:22.190
I have food cooking on the stove.

40:22.190 --> 40:24.710
Listen, show Wanxing around the house.

40:24.710 --> 40:25.800
Or just take a rest.

40:25.840 --> 40:27.030
I'll go make my signature dishes for you.

40:27.030 --> 40:28.630
-Alright.
-Let me help you put these away.

40:28.630 --> 40:30.490
Thanks for such hard work, Uncle.

40:31.440 --> 40:32.750
Well, to be honest,

40:32.750 --> 40:34.110
it does take much hard work to make

40:34.110 --> 40:35.550
my signature dishes for my daughter.

40:35.550 --> 40:36.590
Not a problem at all.

40:36.590 --> 40:37.920
I'll be your assistant.

40:38.320 --> 40:39.940
Are you sure you're up for it
in this suit?

40:39.940 --> 40:40.870
I can take it off.

40:42.250 --> 40:43.250
Let's get to work.

40:44.510 --> 40:45.510
Y-You guys sit down.

40:45.510 --> 40:46.150
Be seated.

40:46.150 --> 40:47.080
You come with me.

40:47.760 --> 40:50.190
You've got this.

40:51.670 --> 40:53.270
Come on, I'll give you a tour.

40:54.550 --> 40:56.110
Are you sure you can manage?

40:56.350 --> 40:57.350
Yes!

40:57.380 --> 40:58.300
What is this?

41:01.150 --> 41:02.280
Feel free to browse.

41:05.250 --> 41:06.690
Is this your room.

41:08.880 --> 41:10.110
I could tell that.

41:16.360 --> 41:18.630
What a spacious room.

41:28.440 --> 41:30.230
Have you always looked so grumpy
since you were little?

41:30.230 --> 41:32.230
It's just that my smiles are subtle.

41:33.770 --> 41:34.900
I have other photos.

41:35.190 --> 41:36.120
Care to see them?

41:36.190 --> 41:36.960
Sure.

41:48.670 --> 41:50.070
Is this you?

41:50.840 --> 41:54.670
I didn't know you used to be a chubby kid.

41:55.830 --> 41:57.360
It was thanks to my grandma.

41:57.710 --> 41:58.590
My grandma's dream grandson

41:58.590 --> 42:00.190
had to be well-fed and plump.

42:03.960 --> 42:05.880
Why is this photo still here?

42:05.920 --> 42:07.510
Move your hand.

42:12.280 --> 42:14.040
Let me see.

42:16.960 --> 42:18.510
Is this also you,

42:18.510 --> 42:20.000
a boy in a princess dress?

42:20.440 --> 42:21.550
Little did I imagine you'd like

42:21.550 --> 42:23.840
to become a princess when you were little.

42:23.840 --> 42:26.530
This is the proof of me being persecuted
by Wang Tian.

42:26.530 --> 42:27.550
Being persecuted?

42:27.550 --> 42:29.070
It seems to me the look suits you well.

42:29.070 --> 42:30.510
A pink bow.

42:30.510 --> 42:31.440
A white tulle gown.

42:31.440 --> 42:32.960
And those Mary Jane shoes.

42:33.590 --> 42:35.190
You look really cute in them.

42:35.960 --> 42:37.760
Rainbow-like long hair,

42:38.000 --> 42:39.510
with eyes resembling jewels.

42:39.510 --> 42:42.770
I think Her Highness
the Shining Star Genius is even cuter.

42:42.880 --> 42:44.320
Why haven't you forgotten it?

42:44.320 --> 42:45.190
I just can't,

42:45.630 --> 42:48.030
for she is so impressive and unforgettable

42:48.030 --> 42:50.830
that the memory about her
is still vivid in my mind.

42:51.070 --> 42:52.030
Fine then.

42:52.030 --> 42:54.000
It's fair to say we have seen each other's

42:54.000 --> 42:55.150
embarrassing past.

42:55.880 --> 42:56.840
We're even now.

42:59.030 --> 43:00.760
Why did you put on those red flowers?

43:00.760 --> 43:03.420
It was all because I was persecuted
by Wang Tian.

43:06.320 --> 43:08.850
You grew up to be
quite a handsome guy, though.

43:35.370 --> 43:36.690
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

43:37.850 --> 43:39.170
♪ Because you're with me ♪
